    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sh-Oligopeptide-110 SP is a single chain human peptide produced synthetically to be identical to a portion of the protein, Neurogenin 1, and contains 13 amino acids consisting of arginine, aspartic acid, glutamic acid, glutamine, glycine and threonine. Neurogenin 1 contains a maximum of 237 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation. It consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
